                  <section>
  <h2>Features</h2>
  
    <ul class="features-graphics">
              <li class="active">
        <a href="/review/533406/what-are-moocs-good-for/">
          <article>
                          <img src="http://www.technologyreview.com/sites/default/files/carousel/moocsx679.jpg" width="679" height="527" alt="" />                        <div class="meta">
                              <h1>Unexpected Benefits of MOOCs</h1>
                                            <p>Online courses may not be changing colleges as their boosters claimed they would, but they can prove valuable in surprising ways.</p>
                                            <h2>By Justin Pope</h2>
                            <p class="cta">Continue</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </a>
      </li>
          <li>
        <a href="/featuredstory/533446/desalination-out-of-desperation/">
          <article>
                          <img src="http://www.technologyreview.com/sites/default/files/carousel/desalx679.jpg" width="679" height="527" alt="" />                        <div class="meta">
                              <h1>Desalination Provides Drought Relief</h1>
                                            <p>Severe droughts are forcing researchers to rethink how technology can increase the supply of fresh water.</p>
                                            <h2>By David Talbot</h2>
                            <p class="cta">Continue</p>
            </div>
          </article>
